title: Significant Moments in U.S. Emergency Medicine, Pt. 2
itunes:title: Significant Moments in U.S. Emergency Medicine, Pt. 2
description:
In this second part of our coverage of emergency care in the U.S., we’ll talk about an important white paper that was a turning point for emergency medicine, the advent of the 9-1-1 service, and the ambulance service that set the model for all others.
